&lt;p&gt;CPR：Cardiopulmonary resuscitation (CPR) 心肺复苏术&lt;br /&gt;
AED：Automated External Defibrillator 自动外置式心脏除颤仪&lt;br /&gt;
VF：Ventricular Fibrillation 心室纤维性颤动&lt;/p&gt;

